videos.description: 1-seed Texas A&M's Jordan Nixon credits 8-seed Tigers' toughness, but said the Aggies found their level of comfort to pull away with the 77-58 victory.
videos.headline: Nixon notes how Aggies overcame LSU's tough play-style

videos.description: Gary Blair credits 8-seed LSU for their dreadful defense, but says the Aggies' poise and patience led them to a 77-58 win as they reach the semifinals to face UGA.
videos.headline: Blair says patience is the reason for 1-seed TAMU's win
